{"tid":434671,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［美瘋搶M記四川醬］女子用一醬換左架車","createTime":"2017-10-13T13:34:17.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-14T11:20:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":79,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":46,"replies":[{"pid":"0d9de79da7ab6078670c9226d6ef3cda8c6da9bb","tid":434671,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:34:17.000Z","msg":"美國麥當勞在當地時間10月7日，以一日限定的方式限量推出19年前配合電影《花木蘭》宣傳的調味醬「川味辣醬」（Szechuan Sauce），但全美只限量1000包，讓不少人排隊購買都撲了空。不少買不到的群眾聚集在麥當勞外抗議，高舉著「給我醬」（Give Us Sauce）的牌子抗議，全美瞬間掀起一股辣醬風潮，沒想到密西根州一名女子就藉著這個機會，在網路上靠著一包小小的辣醬換到一輛轎車。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，住在密西根的瑪莉（Rachel Marie）成為了擁有川味辣醬的幸運兒之一，在辣醬到手之後她在臉書的一個以物易物的交換社團上發文，表示自己想用這包辣醬來換東西，沒想到卻有一名網友基墨（Duane Kimmel）表示他可以用一台2004年出產的福斯GOLF MK4轎車來換，讓不少網友都傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n基墨提出的條件讓瑪莉感到相當驚訝，原以為什麼都換不到的她竟然靠一包小小的辣醬換到一輛車。「感謝這起超狂的交易！我竟然用了一包傳說中的辣醬換到一台福斯GOLF MK4！親愛的基墨，希望你能沉醉在醬汁裡面。」對於為何願意用車來換醬，基墨在事後則是坦言「我就是想吃到那包該死的辣醬」，加上他本來就有另一台車可以開，所以才願意用車來換。<br />\n<br />\n由於消費者對辣醬的反應超乎想像的熱烈，接到許多民眾抱怨的麥當勞只好先公開致歉，接著又表示在下一個冬季就會再推出這款川味辣醬，而且這次不會在搞什麼1日限定，一定讓消費者買好買滿。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20171013005313-260803\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhottopic.chinatimes.com%2F20171013005313-260803&d=kZTSD3bhxdqFI9jV6RfYOnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=07adda42\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hottopic.chinatimes.com/20171013005313-260803</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/213401_0e6a25571cb2ff7b52977d955f80aff2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F213401_0e6a25571cb2ff7b52977d955f80aff2.jpg&h=279cfe8b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/213403_0e6a25571cb2ff7b52977d955f80aff2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F213403_0e6a25571cb2ff7b52977d955f80aff2.jpg&h=2cc2d988&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/10/13/213403_1e3d9f725d28782db90944d689fb9241.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F10%2F13%2F213403_1e3d9f725d28782db90944d689fb9241.jpg&h=42cb4cd2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n誇張"},{"pid":"109219e9ef8b6e07d5147b11f45c671513fb6667","tid":434671,"uid":67237,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:36:19.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"a36e89b7d4989aedab824b19dba1415cce1ac0ac","tid":434671,"uid":5253,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:36:59.000Z","msg":"04年車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93b2b391d56cc21a174fa92b1a3a0c613d37da69","tid":434671,"uid":12991,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T13:46:14.000Z","msg":"有四川醬有女屌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c30ad39c6d7c3345c726372128afa93d0970edbf","tid":434671,"uid":31215,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"人多有白痴..."},{"pid":"9c79a6e707cddb873e8dedabde6da9248088a6b0","tid":434671,"uid":139967,"like":22,"dislike":1,"score":21,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:31:25.000Z","msg":"Rick n Morty<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e1fae0d4a903b544a3067f3d50dc1c137e20fc3","tid":434671,"uid":85163,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:33:18.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"82b8629cb8dd8b5b53138ffd0ba3617aa55858d6","tid":434671,"uid":60366,"like":178,"dislike":2,"score":176,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>人多有白痴...</blockquote><br />\n無話白唔白痴<br />\n兩條友都開心你理得人咁多<br />\n更何況嗰條仔根本唔志在架車<br />\n分分鐘係有錢仔黎"},{"pid":"3802f2b416842b9b6f69e122b217aa5ecb11256e","tid":434671,"uid":65530,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-13T14:46:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"851c660e84a37e5c422203cf2ec7c684e6d614c9","tid":434671,"uid":51269,"like":71,"dislike":0,